Class Fibonacci

  • java.lang.Object
    • ps0.Fibonacci

  • public class Fibonacci
extends java.lang.Object
    Fibonacci calculates the nth term in the Fibonacci sequence. The first two terms of the Fibonacci sequence are both 1, and each subsequent term is the sum of the previous two terms.

    mbolin
